{"body":"[{\"data\":1,\"prerenderedAt\":110},[\"ShallowReactive\",2],{\"project-en-\\u002Fprojects\\u002Fquizzer-ai-interview-system\":3},{\"id\":4,\"title\":5,\"architecture\":6,\"body\":7,\"category\":81,\"challenge\":82,\"company\":83,\"description\":84,\"extension\":85,\"featured\":86,\"meta\":87,\"metrics\":88,\"navigation\":86,\"order\":95,\"path\":96,\"period\":97,\"results\":98,\"role\":99,\"seo\":100,\"stack\":101,\"status\":107,\"stem\":108,\"__hash__\":109},\"projects_en\\u002Fen\\u002Fprojects\\u002Fquizzer-ai-interview-system.md\",\"QuizzerA — AI Interview System\",\"Built a GPT-powered interview assistant as a Spring Boot microservice. The system captured interview transcripts, generated structured feedback using custom GPT prompts, and routed results through an event-driven pipeline via Apache Kafka. A follow-up scheduler automated the next steps — no manual triage needed.\",{\"type\":8,\"value\":9,\"toc\":74},\"minimark\",[10,15,19,23,26,55,59],[11,12,14],\"h2\",{\"id\":13},\"challenge\",\"Challenge\",[16,17,18],\"p\",{},\"Interview feedback at scale was the bottleneck. With hundreds of candidates across multiple clients, interviewers spent more time documenting than evaluating. Feedback quality varied wildly between interviewers — some wrote paragraphs, others wrote bullet points. Candidates waited up to a week for results.\",[11,20,22],{\"id\":21},\"architecture\",\"Architecture\",[16,24,25],{},\"The system was built as a Spring Boot microservice integrated into the existing Globant hiring platform:\",[27,28,29,37,43,49],\"ol\",{},[30,31,32,36],\"li\",{},[33,34,35],\"strong\",{},\"Transcript capture\",\" — Interview recordings transcribed via a speech-to-text service, sent to the microservice via REST\",[30,38,39,42],{},[33,40,41],{},\"GPT processing\",\" — Custom GPT prompts evaluated transcripts against role-specific rubrics, generating structured JSON feedback\",[30,44,45,48],{},[33,46,47],{},\"Event pipeline\",\" — Results published to Apache Kafka topics, consumed by the notification service and the follow-up scheduler\",[30,50,51,54],{},[33,52,53],{},\"Follow-up automation\",\" — A scheduled job checked pending feedback, sent reminders, and escalated stale items\",[11,56,58],{\"id\":57},\"results\",\"Results\",[60,61,62,65,68,71],\"ul\",{},[30,63,64],{},\"Feedback cycle reduced from 5 business days to under 48 hours\",[30,66,67],{},\"Interview throughput tripled — same team handled 3x candidate volume\",[30,69,70],{},\"Feedback consistency improved — GPT-enforced structure eliminated ad-hoc formatting\",[30,72,73],{},\"Hiring manager satisfaction up — structured JSON enabled dashboard analytics\",{\"title\":75,\"searchDepth\":76,\"depth\":76,\"links\":77},\"\",2,[78,79,80],{\"id\":13,\"depth\":76,\"text\":14},{\"id\":21,\"depth\":76,\"text\":22},{\"id\":57,\"depth\":76,\"text\":58},\"ai\",\"Interview feedback was slow, inconsistent, and manual. Candidates waited days for results. Interviewers spent hours writing notes.\",\"Globant\",\"Customized GPT for key projects and developed an interview follow-up system to enhance feedback and efficiency\",\"md\",true,{},[89,92],{\"label\":90,\"value\":91},\"Feedback cycle\",\"-60%\",{\"label\":93,\"value\":94},\"Interview throughput\",\"+3x\",1,\"\\u002Fen\\u002Fprojects\\u002Fquizzer-ai-interview-system\",\"2022-2024\",\"Reduced feedback cycle from 5 days to under 48 hours. Tripled interview throughput per interviewer. Standardized feedback quality across teams.\",\"Java Microservices Developer\",{\"title\":5,\"description\":84},[102,103,104,105,106],\"Java\",\"Spring Boot\",\"GPT\",\"AI\",\"Microservices\",\"shipped\",\"en\\u002Fprojects\\u002Fquizzer-ai-interview-system\",\"ilk2GEbp36Ki7x5RFvm_FOu90oWcY_r0F0bD_n74XBY\",1783828259339]","statusCode":200,"statusMessage":"","headers":{"content-type":"application/json;charset=utf-8","x-powered-by":"Nuxt"}}